The wedding would be late next year at a destination venue (likely in the Caribbean).
The wrinkle here is that his guests are wealthier and would be the ones likely attending the destination wedding.
Plus, millions of Americans’ jobs have vanished in the past few weeks, so even your wealthier guests may have real trouble attending the kind of wedding you’re imagining.
